{"tid":2100501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿主席無視警阻救援  400救護員「過檔」新工會","createTime":"2020-07-09T05:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T13:32:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b6763745baeba7bf4e02d8d5072b587450fa8b53","tid":2100501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/ZGAE4JWYTWAB5GES2X5RDT6HNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FZGAE4JWYTWAB5GES2X5RDT6HNY%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=52a5e034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200709%2FZGAE4JWYTWAB5GES2X5RDT6HNY%2F&h=883ae891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200709/ZGAE4JWYTWAB5GES2X5RDT6HNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不滿主席無視警阻救援 <br />\n400救護員「過檔」新工會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kvOIzunK9WP9VvWpXiX8JyrMYsw=/510x327/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUXZGIKPOB34OULZVU5FDCVGI4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkvOIzunK9WP9VvWpXiX8JyrMYsw%3D%2F510x327%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRUXZGIKPOB34OULZVU5FDCVGI4.gif&h=54a7393c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救護員會爆辭任潮，有指因主席無批評警阻救援；圖為8.31救護員未能進入港鐵站內救人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】消防處五大傳統工會之一、<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：設水馬陣 限制傳媒  國安署「高牆」內鬼祟揭幕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四理事辭任<br />\n<br />\n根據消防處救護員會網站，2019至21年度共有15名理事會委員。本報獲悉，最近有多達四名理事以「私人理由」辭任，包括副主席（常務）黃鐵樑、康樂福利陳霆讚，以及理事柳健輝和袁洛文。<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報曾聯絡部份辭任理事，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n故已於上月27日辭任理事一職。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向本報透露，工會今次辭任潮由積怨所起，包括對該會主席李偉孝的政治立場不滿，以及工會就爭取救護員福祉的不作為。據指，李偉孝去年11月接受《大公報》訪問時，狠批抗爭者「暴徒打人成癮」、阻礙救援；惟對警方作為，包括屢次阻礙救援等卻隻字未提，當時已引起工會中人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有約400名救護員因不滿工會作風，已「過檔」至本年初成立的「香港消防救護控制組人員聯合工會」。<br />\n<br />\n香港消防處救護員會1970年正式註冊，目前會員人數逾2,000人。政府紀律部隊人員總工會上月底發聲明支持港版國安法，消防處救護員會亦為聯署成員團體之一。"},{"pid":"21956cc8d8189b9c2714ffb16f768dfc080d1fb4","tid":2100501,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542d8d7d9449c5bc69da5bdd5b7f014edd5989b4","tid":2100501,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇風班奶共嘅救護消防幾時做特務狗"},{"pid":"faf2528d9eb50e2f2c8fec38337f60f66222ab1f","tid":2100501,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98926248ba610a558b535bef2e59342ff1314bfe","tid":2100501,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"faf2528d9eb50e2f2c8fec38337f60f66222ab1f","tid":2100501,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"7月11,12日（六，日） 0900-2100 去票站投票<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100511</a>"},{"pid":"ac8c9c5ae7d46ac65213f0004e470217a794c5de","tid":2100501,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"話時話831最後有冇死到人"},{"pid":"2f4b115ebe5bee8d2ef1ca1d9f7a2dd74774ca9e","tid":2100501,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score